  "text": "Chemical Inhibition in HLMs. Gemfibrozil glucuronidation in pooled HLMs was measured in the absence and presence of either mefenamic acid [CITATION_1] or racemic flurbiprofen [CITATION_2] , two potent inhibitors for UGT2B7. To determine the IC 50 values of these inhibitors, gemfibrozil (1 M) was incubated in the absence and presence of either mefenamic acid (0.1-10 M) or flurbiprofen (1-100 M). Incubation was performed for 10 min using a protein concentration of 0.1 mg of protein/ml.",
